description: The first ever in-depth analysis of the tactics and equipment used by the heroes and villains of the Star Wars universe has arrived! Including detailed examples from Earth’s military history, best-selling author George Beahm illustrates how a merciless empire managed to subdue a galaxy with the application of overwhelming force and technology, and how a ragtag group of rebels could cobble together enough of a punch to topple a seemingly unbeatable enemy.
